We set up the fishing trip and went out and had the best time with Rick, a disabled veteran from Edgewater, Florida. Rick served our country and in return, we got to serve him with this awesome fishing experience!

Thank you Rick for your service to our country and for blessing us with this opportunity to serve you with this fun day of fishing!
